submission.1.player.additional_feedback: I was confident at first but as the game went on I became more influenced by the others but then if the majority of us got it wrong, I became disillusioned and decided to stick with my own decisions and ignore theirs. So, of course, they started to seem to be more correct than me, so I changed my strategy back to agreeing with them...to no avail!!! Fun to do and I enjoyed it, even though I lost out on any bonus lol. No problems or glitches at all with the study. Very well conducted.
